org.ojai

Class FieldPathBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ojai.FieldPathBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, FieldPathListener

    public class FieldPathBaseListener
extends Object
implements FieldPathListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of FieldPathListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
